{"tid":750971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"而家成科地理比考評局搞到不倫不類","createTime":"2018-07-21T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T13:25:14.000Z","uid":192234,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8a63a9ffb932e03745110c568f2c808b0afd980e","tid":750971,"uid":192234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">考評局你無撚病呀</span><br />\n<br />\n下年地理DSE開始，會增加多一條18分嘅必答題，而問嘅嘢自係單純圍繞field trip <a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/geog/GEOG-SampleFieldwork-basedQuest-C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FSubject_Information%2Fgeog%2FGEOG-SampleFieldwork-basedQuest-C.pdf&d=6bvjaSOZCT5YRZrG%2BCcGUnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ce4a932f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/geog/GEOG-SampleFieldwork-basedQuest-C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n睇番份樣本試卷，問啲問題對啲學生地理嘅學習係無撚幫助，只不過係一尾問啲咩好壞處同field trip要用嘅工具，鬼唔知冬天條河乾咗做唔到field trip咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲問題只會額外增加咗佢哋要溫嘅書，同埋比補習佬多個藉口吸引佢哋9補地理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> field trip係重要，但係而家啲老師已經好多嘢教冇乜時間剩，唔通加多條field trip題就會令到佢哋去多啲field trip?對學生將來就業/升學又冇用，多啲嘢要背只會對學生學地理嘅興趣減低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇番而家地理專少少嘅concept其實唔多，好多都係通識性質，你係課程加番多啲專啲嘅concept仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有其實考評局之前已經成日搏大霧想係2014同下年地理加sba，根本好多人都覺得多9餘，又加重學生壓力（有機構做過問卷<a href=\"http://www1.hkga.org/download/SBA_CCLam.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkga.org%2Fdownload%2FSBA_CCLam.pdf&d=6bvjaSOZCT5YRZrG%2BCcGUnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1646a9d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkga.org/download/SBA_CCLam.pdf</a>），實事唔見你做，淨係識盲目加sba，你啲專家可唔可以用下腦先改課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b2c2c224088ec7748b43ad10ac1e272e9c30b0","tid":750971,"uid":11417,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8e090bd672ca43152154e3dabf0a001e2b32d98","tid":750971,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"2014<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6455b4a229059d844e082044cefc650a6685eb4","tid":750971,"uid":192234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8e090bd672ca43152154e3dabf0a001e2b32d98","tid":750971,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"2014<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/203406_6ebd6145655f815a89071f0cd0ce2a72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F203406_6ebd6145655f815a89071f0cd0ce2a72.png&h=9c63d13a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b37d5b3eefad852c62c310a6d465d37c41ac2dd1","tid":750971,"uid":192234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"63b2c2c224088ec7748b43ad10ac1e272e9c30b0","tid":750971,"uid":11417,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得學點樣field trip係某程度都幾有用，尤其是如果上到u都係想讀地理，但係就係加多條field trip題令到paper 2嘅比重少咗，學生投嘅時間精力喺electives就會少咗，而個人覺得electives正正係真正學到嘢嘅課題，而且好多技巧都係dbq/mc都有考學生，冇咩必要要加field trip題"},{"pid":"664c9220e7249711e703f9a8c59aef9da0825107","tid":750971,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a9d1c44e9d21adfba5507a04adbf4c5e163beaf","tid":750971,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"cite